txt.en: Spiders, angered by invaders to the Drúadan Forest, search for prey on the forest floor. You suspect many could fall victim to the traps laid by these creatures. These spiders should be dealt with quickly.
You have defeated many spiders in Taur Drúadan.

Spiders can be found in the woods of Taur Drúadan.\n\nYou should defeat spiders in Taur Drúadan.
Angered spiders search the forest floor for prey and should be dealt with before any forest-folk fall victim to the spiders' webs.
